867
00:38:57,480 --> 00:38:59,170
Huayan Airport Customs, Binhai,

868
00:39:00,070 --> 00:39:01,170
was awarded third-class merit.

869
00:39:01,480 --> 00:39:02,050
Which class?

870
00:39:02,590 --> 00:39:03,740
Third-class!

871
00:39:05,480 --> 00:39:07,300
Good! Third-class merit.

872
00:39:09,710 --> 00:39:11,130
My trainee is the best.

873
00:39:14,840 --> 00:39:15,650
One day,

874
00:39:16,190 --> 00:39:17,380
when I'm old and gray,

875
00:39:18,150 --> 00:39:19,010
worn out,

876
00:39:19,880 --> 00:39:21,090
stuck in bed,

877
00:39:21,480 --> 00:39:22,610
can't see,

878
00:39:22,630 --> 00:39:23,530
can't hear,

879
00:39:24,550 --> 00:39:25,610
you come find me

880
00:39:25,840 --> 00:39:27,260
with news like this

881
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:28,460
and read it out loud,

882
00:39:28,960 --> 00:39:30,980
let the old folks next door

883
00:39:31,230 --> 00:39:31,940
turn green with envy.

884
00:39:32,520 --> 00:39:33,170
Let them eat their hearts out!

885
00:39:33,840 --> 00:39:34,380
You hear me?

886
00:39:35,110 --> 00:39:35,610
I hear you.

887
00:39:36,480 --> 00:39:37,130
You hear me?

888
00:39:37,150 --> 00:39:37,860
I hear you!

889
00:39:38,710 --> 00:39:39,740
Good then.

890
00:39:42,320 --> 00:39:43,090
That's all I needed.

891
00:39:44,590 --> 00:39:46,460
Don't forget what you promised me.

892
00:39:46,920 --> 00:39:47,860
Guard the border.

893
00:39:49,510 --> 00:39:50,260
I will.

894
00:39:53,800 --> 00:39:57,720
[Four Years Later; 2023]

895
00:40:23,030 --> 00:40:23,820
Thank you, Fei.

896
00:40:34,230 --> 00:40:35,780
You went to see your mentor?

897
00:40:36,840 --> 00:40:37,860
How's he doing?

898
00:40:40,710 --> 00:40:42,260
How'd you know I went to see him?

899
00:40:43,880 --> 00:40:45,740
Otherwise,

900
00:40:46,040 --> 00:40:48,010
why would you crave my noodles?

901
00:40:53,070 --> 00:40:54,690
He's doing alright physically.

902
00:40:55,630 --> 00:40:57,610
It's just his memory's getting worse.

903
00:40:57,840 --> 00:40:59,010
So much has slipped away.

904
00:41:00,920 --> 00:41:02,300
Last time I saw him,

905
00:41:03,230 --> 00:41:05,530
the only thing he remembered
was the noodles I made.

906
00:41:05,880 --> 00:41:07,610
Still wolfed it down like always.

907
00:41:11,480 --> 00:41:12,740
Then again,
maybe forgetting isn't so bad.

908
00:41:13,710 --> 00:41:14,860
All these years,

909
00:41:15,590 --> 00:41:16,900
there's a lot worth forgetting.

910
00:41:22,920 --> 00:41:23,570
Fei,

911
00:41:25,110 --> 00:41:26,050
honestly,

912
00:41:27,360 --> 00:41:29,010
I'm kinda scared he'll forget me.

913
00:41:32,880 --> 00:41:33,490
Cong,

914
00:41:34,230 --> 00:41:35,740
you carry him in your heart,

915
00:41:36,230 --> 00:41:37,610
I carry him in mine.

916
00:41:37,630 --> 00:41:38,530
Isn't that enough?

917
00:41:39,480 --> 00:41:41,980
You've got to carry on his work.

918
00:41:42,960 --> 00:41:44,010
That's what matters most.

919
00:41:45,480 --> 00:41:46,090
I know.

920
00:41:50,840 --> 00:41:52,820
Oh, I've got something to tell you.

921
00:41:53,440 --> 00:41:55,170
I've got a trainee now.

922
00:41:59,230 --> 00:42:00,460
How's it going?

923
00:42:00,880 --> 00:42:01,940
Bring them by sometime.

924
00:42:02,000 --> 00:42:03,300
I'll make them a bowl of noodles.

925
00:42:03,630 --> 00:42:04,010
Deal.

926
00:42:11,030 --> 00:42:12,570
You all, one generation after another,

927
00:42:12,800 --> 00:42:14,210
have to hold your post.

928
00:42:14,520 --> 00:42:16,170
Train your trainee right,

929
00:42:16,440 --> 00:42:17,690
and stay safe.

930
00:42:20,110 --> 00:42:20,900
Don't worry.

931
00:42:21,510 --> 00:42:22,420
As long as we're on our post,

932
00:42:22,960 --> 00:42:23,900
it's like Mentor never left.

933
00:43:30,800 --> 00:43:37,440
♪There's a place of simple,
everyday warmth♪

934
00:43:38,280 --> 00:43:45,000
♪A door left open
for the wandering soul♪

935
00:43:45,920 --> 00:43:52,440
♪A humble table still warm with love♪

936
00:43:52,640 --> 00:43:56,360
♪After you've tasted every high and low♪

937
00:43:56,560 --> 00:44:00,240
♪Come home, I'll keep you warm♪

938
00:44:00,960 --> 00:44:07,680
♪Where the days begin and end♪

939
00:44:08,400 --> 00:44:15,320
♪A light still on for the ones
who've lost their way♪

940
00:44:16,120 --> 00:44:22,680
♪An embrace waiting just for you♪

941
00:44:22,960 --> 00:44:26,680
♪Through every passing season♪

942
00:44:26,760 --> 00:44:30,640
♪Even if you return with nothing at all♪

943
00:44:31,080 --> 00:44:34,600
♪Turn around and look♪

944
00:44:34,800 --> 00:44:38,600
♪That door's still open♪

945
00:44:38,800 --> 00:44:42,440
♪A light still burning♪

946
00:44:42,520 --> 00:44:46,240
♪Waiting there for you♪

947
00:44:46,440 --> 00:44:49,920
♪Turn around and look♪

948
00:44:50,160 --> 00:44:54,000
♪Someone's still waiting♪

949
00:44:54,120 --> 00:44:57,760
♪Watching the dusk settle in♪

950
00:44:57,840 --> 00:45:01,560
♪Waiting for the break of dawn♪

951
00:45:03,320 --> 00:45:07,000
♪It's always there♪
